Tumhara Rock–Paper–Scissors project abhi ek basic functional game hai (UI + score + localStorage). Ab isme tum kuch new features add karke ise aur interactive aur professional bana sakte ho.

🔥 Advanced Features jo add kar sakte ho:
🎮 Gameplay Features

Best of 5 / Best of 10 Mode

Ek option do jisme user choose kare ki game ek round khele ya “Best of 5” ho.

Example: pehle jo 3 jeetega, wo winner.

Levels / Difficulty

Easy Mode → Computer random move karega.

Hard Mode → Computer “predictive AI” use karega (user ke last 2-3 moves track karke guess karega).

Player vs Player (PvP Mode)

2 players ek hi device pe khelen (ek player choose kare, fir dusra choose kare).

Ya online socket.io use karke multiplayer ban jaaye.

🎨 UI/UX Enhancements

Animations

Har move ke liye animation (jaise rock shake kare, scissors cut kare, paper flip ho).

Winner ka icon thoda zoom-in aur glow effect ke saath dikhaye.

Sound Effects

Rock, paper, scissors ke alag-alag sound effects.

Jeetne / harne pe chhota victory / defeat sound.

Theme Switcher (Dark / Light Mode)

Ek toggle button jisse user game ka theme change kar sake.

📊 Tracking & Fun

Leaderboard / High Score

LocalStorage ya Firebase me sabse zyada jeetne wala score save ho.

Game Statistics

User ki overall performance show karo:

Win %

Most chosen move (Rock/Paper/Scissors)

Computer vs User ka ratio

Timer Mode

Ek timer do (e.g. 5 sec) jisme user ko move choose karna hoga.

Agar choose nahi kare to automatic “lose” count ho jaaye.

🤖 Smart Additions

AI Opponent (Learning Computer)

Computer track kare ki user jyada rock/paper/scissors khelta hai aur uske against move play kare.

Example: agar user jyada "rock" choose karta hai → computer jyada "paper" choose karega.

Voice Commands 🎙️

User bole “rock”, “paper” ya “scissors” aur game usko input le. (Web Speech API use karke).

Mobile Friendly Responsive Design

Buttons bada aur touch friendly ho mobile pe.

👉 Suggestion: Agar tum beginner → intermediate level project banana chahte ho, to mai recommend karta hu:

Best of 5 mode

Sound effects

Animations (winner highlight with glow/zoom)

Statistics page

Ye 4 cheezein add kar doge to project bahut unique aur professional lagne lagega. 🚀

❓Kya tum chahte ho mai pehle Best of 5 mode + winner animation (glow/zoom) ka code add karke du tumhare current project me?